_comment: All DAF sites or features are controlled by DAF MVP feature flag: msWalletCheckoutDeepAutofill. The used DAF whitelist keys are defined as follow:
default:  Shipped One Page DAF Sites

selfhost: One Page DAF Sites including both whitelisted and not-whitelisted sites, as long as address line 1 and card number are found on one Page. This was the scenario EC shipped at 2023/6/14 which doubles the DAU

startup', 'beyond99_path1', and 'recovering_online_sites': are the 3 phases when we bring back DAF sites patch by patch. It all refers to one page scenario with different traffic allocation. please refer to EC DAF CFR Pool design for details.
multiple_page:  target for experiment on DAF across page scenarios
shipped_multiplePage: shipped multiple Page DAF sites
